{"sections":[],"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Apple LLVM compiler has evolved at a staggering pace, providing remarkably quick compile times and generating lightning-fast code. See how Xcode integrates LLVM into the IDE to alert to you mistakes as you type, and how it can even fix problems for you. Learn how Xcode’s static analyzer leverages the intelligence of the LLVM engine, and see the latest advancements in C++ support."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-316-LLVM-Technologies-in-Depth","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-316-llvm-technologies-in-depth"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/316\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode","title":"LLVM Technologies in Depth"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}],"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null},"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/316/":{"type":"dow